Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast! Image Credit: UCSB Physics

Name: Montara State Beach
Description: A popular beach for fishing and tidepooling close to Half Moon Bay. This is my favorite beach to visit with my family, we go every time that I'm home! Image Credit: Jim Musil (Painter)

Name: Pinnacles National Park
Description: California's youngest National Park. This is also my favorite national park, I love hiking through the caves and sitting by the reservoir. Image Credit: National Geographic

Name: Peet's Coffee in Saratoga
Description: A quiet, cozy coffee shop in Saratoga. In highschool, my friends and I would always come here to study. Image Credit: MapQuest

Name: Rancho San Antonio Preserve
Description: One of the most popular recreational areas in Santa Clara County for hiking and biking. My sister and I love hiking here to watch the sunset. Image Credit: AllTrails

Name: Santana Row
Description: The best mall and eateriers in the San Jose area! Image Credit: Wikipedia
